                    <h2>Alternatives to Emergency Loans For Unemployed Single Mothers </h2>
                    <p>If emergency loans don’t meet your expectations, some alternative programs for single parents may be appealing to you. Unlike traditional loans, they are free to use and easy to get. If you have lost hope of getting financial help, consider the following options.</p>
                    <ul>
